145
00:07:10,070 --> 00:07:12,450
Our truck was hijacked by some defeated Japanese soldiers

146
00:07:12,450 --> 00:07:14,190
near the border in Wanding

147
00:07:14,220 --> 00:07:16,300
when we came back from Burma.

148
00:07:22,530 --> 00:07:23,970
By Japanese soldiers?

149
00:07:24,000 --> 00:07:24,800
Yes.

150
00:07:25,050 --> 00:07:27,010
They killed both drivers.

151
00:07:27,870 --> 00:07:28,910
Then,

152
