229
00:10:48,500 --> 00:10:50,080
you'll end up like Dad.

230
00:10:50,240 --> 00:10:51,680
I know what you mean.

231
00:10:52,770 --> 00:10:53,890
You want me

232
00:10:54,390 --> 00:10:55,680
to leave the NBIS

233
00:10:56,540 --> 00:10:58,400
and live a peaceful life with you,

234
00:10:58,940 --> 00:10:59,670
